<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٢ ... سُورَةُ البَقَرَة ... آياتها ٢٨٦ مدنية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{آلم}</span> ... هَذَا القُرْآنُ مُؤَلَّفٌ مِنْ هَذِهِ الْحُرُوفِ، وَلَا يَسْتَطِيعُونَ الإِتْيَانَ بِمِثْلِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِّلْمُتَّقِينَ}</span> ... مَنْ جَعَلُوا بَيْنَهُمْ وَبَيْنَ عَذَابِ اللهِ وِقَايَةً بِفِعْلِ الأَوَامِرِ وَتَرْكِ النَّوَاهِي.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَتَمَ اللهُ}</span> ... طَبَعَ اللهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غِشَاوَةٌ}</span> ... غِطَاءٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّرَضٌ}</span> ... شَكٌّ، وَنِفَاقٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيَمُدُّهُمْ}</span> ... يَزِيدُهُمْ، وَيُمْهِلُهُمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَعْمَهُونَ}</span> ... يَتَحَيَّرُونَ، وَيَعْمَوْنَ عَنِ الرُّشْدِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بُكْمٌ}</span> ... لَا يَنْطِقُونَ بِالْحَقِّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَصَيِّبٍ}</span> ... كَمَطَرٍ شَدِيدٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَندَادًا}</span> ... نُظَرَاءَ، وَأَمْثَالًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَيْبٍ}</span> ... شَكٍّ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُتَشَابِهًا}</span> ... فِي اللَّونِ، وَالْمَنْظَرِ، لَا فِي الطَّعْمِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اسْتَوَى}</span> ... قَصَدَ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>